reviewText:
THIS IS THE DVD EVERY AMERICAN FAN WANTS!!!... MAKE MORE = MAKE MORE MONEY!!!
SOMEONE NEEDS TO GET ON THIS!!!... I MEAN SERIOUSLY!!!

I never got the chance to see Silverchair. So when I found this I had to order it. This is a great concert dvd, not all of them are, and Silverchair put on an outstanding performance. I would recommend this to anyone who likes this band.
